content.body: I once visited a mutual friend of @domenic while they were undergrads at caltech and was shown a fire extinguisher that had been labeled in sharpie: rogdort, anti-burninator
Though, notably, we did not know we were mutuals until long after domenic had been working with me on Q promises. Life finds a way

ServiceNow has had in its Chicago office (my home base) a roughly three foot tall drawing of Trogdor on a whiteboard you have to go out of your way to find. But, 5 years on, it still remains.  Even the building janitorial staff respects his power.
It is one of my favorite bits of office culture ever
